        {
            "title": "〈車用電子展〉360°MOBILITY Mega Shows落幕 貿協：後續商機上看3.38億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mZKcMbLzwNLMnJox9z12aQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/d34e357d534ae4ee69d4aac2eed864bd\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%8A%E7%94%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%B1%95-360-mobility-mega-shows%E8%90%BD%E5%B9%95-110638587.html",
