        {
            "title": "企業出海｜再有國內連鎖快餐店攻港 「華萊士」開首分店 首店落戶九龍城廣場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Yp.3VZQ7ECUVdxAOPC_gJg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/1d1b7fcccf57e8181f0bc42392f192da\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近年多間內地連鎖餐飲品牌來港開設分店，有網民發現內地連鎖西式快餐店巨頭「<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"華萊士\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:華萊士;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華萊士\">華萊士</a>」來香港開設首間分店，將會選址在<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"九龍城廣場\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:九龍城廣場;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/九龍城廣場\">九龍城廣場</a>預計五月開店。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「華萊士」在國內被稱為「中國版肯德基」，為一間連鎖的西式快餐店，主要提供包括漢堡、炸雞等套餐，定位以「高性價比」作為賣點，與另一攻港品牌「德克士」類似。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據網民提供的資料，分店將會選址在九龍城廣場B2層，此舖位原本為另一連鎖快餐店「大快活」，舖位已經圍板並寫有「華萊士隆重入駐香港九龍城廣場」字眼。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4294cd35-ecf6-3c6a-a217-4a482bbed493-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">帖文引起網民討論，但對於選址和食物質素進行調侃較多，如「呢個場…佢加油」、「呢間嘢喺內地都好似麻麻喎」、「要試下佢嘅招牌噴射套餐」、「食完會變噴射戰士」。小紅書亦有內地網民稱「太好了，香港有便秘的人有福了！」、「香港朋友們也可以感受一下通暢的感覺了」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華萊士在國內多次被傳出食品安全問題，如出現後廚衛生不達標、炸雞掉在地上繼續油炸售賣等。因此被網民稱為「噴射戰士」，因曾有消費者反映在華萊士用餐後容易腹瀉。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%87%BA%E6%B5%B7-%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%80%A3%E9%8E%96%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E5%BA%97%E6%94%BB%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8F%AF%E8%90%8A%E5%A3%AB-%E9%96%8B%E9%A6%96%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97-%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%97%E8%90%BD%E6%88%B6%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%9F%8E%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4-094538166.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 17:55:03",
